Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在的感想是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.70,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於明天的啟動儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在的感想是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.40,0:02:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全長6358千米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿特斯拉級宇宙航行宇宙船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.60,0:02:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丟卡利翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需補給就能獨自航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能進行空間跳躍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還具有對星球進行環境改造的功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.90,0:02:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是它的用途是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了達成我們人類的最終目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.90,0:02:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,製造一個神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人親自創造出造物主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人? 你是說貴族吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像妳不把貴族當人看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴族不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是地球人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.80,0:02:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.60,0:03:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}注: Eclair 法語有閃電之意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.60,0:03:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我的名字Eclair一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從我失去能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.40,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有數據看就無法做接待和嚮導的工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我們還是用雨傘或是納米屏障吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是提個建議啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.50,0:04:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳必須要好好地補償我喔 小Lumi
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,補償?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也擅長這種戰法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola 怎麼現在說這個呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.90,0:04:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐要一百萬次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是午餐的話 要三百萬次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會找妳請客的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 非常樂意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先說在前 我是認真的 一百萬次!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來地毯比以前的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有沙發也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一點也讓我很煩惱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是讓我聽聽關於事件的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫那姊弟倆過去吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.90,0:05:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,護送啟動儀式用之香檳酒的重要任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那兩個人是我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我是妳的耳朵嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情報費是很貴的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我已經付給你的搭擋足夠的費用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是什麼都瞞不了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.60,0:05:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天即將啟動的阿特拉斯級宇宙間航行宇宙船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丟卡利翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.90,0:05:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,負責資金調度的是GOTT的開發基金綜合事務局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是它耗掉了宇宙行星聯盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾百年份的綜合資金啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.90,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5000個企業、財團和國家貢獻的資產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.30,0:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴族的愛好實在是奢侈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 對他們而言是投資
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就有完全回收的辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.20,0:05:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行星改造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 透過環境改造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以像源源不斷製造不動產資產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是會下金蛋的鵝一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為這對經濟會有一個負面的衝擊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不向他們對外宣稱的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丟卡利翁果然還是正如其名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}注: 丟卡利翁--希神 建造了方舟 相當於聖經中的諾亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一艘方舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.70,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以認為是一致通過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.90,0:06:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們解除行星聯盟經濟署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇巴耶特．多托利修克的職務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及解除他的銀河通商關稅機構長官的職務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個多托利修克啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 到現在已經製造了很多麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是該撤換掉他的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.80,0:06:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個丟卡利翁已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好是一個不錯時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來接替他的位置 如何呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.20,0:07:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種工作不適合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.60,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶來您要的紀錄了 局長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 Vendredi
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紀錄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.00,0:07:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 是到目前為止的GOTT的紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我這樣的人看 可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 因為你已經都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔啊 真是不留情面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政治交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司法交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有收買企業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要經濟爭端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在擴大成局部戰爭前就已經解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT做的不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是他一個人的功績喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們根本管不著的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是說他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你們兩個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用606線路聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是直接來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們帶來給你一個訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多托利修克大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.10,0:08:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛在行星聯盟評議會樞機委員會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.20,0:08:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除您的行星聯盟經濟署以及GOTT長官的職務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.10,0:08:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡從這裡眺望的景色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我深感意外呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還活著的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.10,0:08:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你們的僱主不只有我而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 雖然我不喜歡被別人利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是處世之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還蠻聰明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.10,0:09:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是成熟的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.20,0:09:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是GOTT的另一面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.30,0:09:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這些是行星聯盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是貴族交給GOTT的工作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您應該知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生中十有八九的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.20,0:09:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你知道也無可奈何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼給我看這個呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棟新建的大樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好像沒什麼差別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.70,0:10:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻強化成能連接Aineias的全部網絡系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼妳就能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.10,0:10:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我什麼也辦不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳要快點讓身體恢復到原來的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訊息只有這一個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.80,0:10:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 我想把訊息直接傳給本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 這沒啥兩樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一條非常可靠的機密線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在到底在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有必要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過早晚會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是報信者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交出鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.80,0:11:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交出GOTT長官獨有的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊交出來 然後離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以活久一點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是他們的訊息嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.70,0:11:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經充分傳達了客戶的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訊息確實傳達了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.20,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最後一次在這裡看風景了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,la Lu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me...Mercredi
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.80,0:12:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前妳都待在哪裡呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳在上次事件之後就失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.90,0:12:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有連絡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.70,0:12:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 la 發生了很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 眼鏡還有頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差點就認不出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.60,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆也完全變了另一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也發生了很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.70,0:13:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 Lumiere?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.30,0:13:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在這裡聊也不是辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.00,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 我今天只是代為轉達一個消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消息?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才起就怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.60,0:13:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說那個Mercredi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mer嗎? 她的確有些奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.60,0:13:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表面的東西是微不足道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.20,0:13:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據這個資料 Mercredi由於生死不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經從職員名單中去除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她應該是被當作一般訪客來對待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但卻不經過我們接待台而出現在那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不覺得這裡面有特殊的原因嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.20,0:14:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 妳不覺得她帶來的消息令人在意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快到局長室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個...為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.10,0:14:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.30,0:14:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局長 ES成員Eclair和Lumiere來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她們進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經早先一步在這裡打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.30,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就如妳所見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.30,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是GOTT的工作清單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.70,0:14:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是地下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclipse 這些是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看清楚了 Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.50,0:15:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些不是經過局長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.00,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是在長官的命令下執行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.70,0:15:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇巴耶特．多托利修克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 明天見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.60,0:16:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們放學後竟然要馬上去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們自己也想工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了他們自己呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.60,0:16:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是學校又可以重新開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.90,0:16:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是托了羅森費爾特財團的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴族們也不完全都是壞人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還不能對他們失去戒心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 又要模仿法利先生的話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天可以就先這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂姆 又是你啊!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以呀 蒂姆 可以離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂姆錫大人 請答應我這是您最後一次來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.70,0:16:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 不過我想繼續做到學校完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的預定是和總理的聯誼會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.00,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上八點有一個和貿易聯盟的會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.10,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我們要在當地時間晚上九點抵達第二大陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在經濟理事會確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.70,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並簽訂第一次協議書以及相關條款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.00,0:17:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair小姐 這顆星球現在已經沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將會以一個獨立國家的狀態努力下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過有一些麻煩呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我們解決了一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.40,0:17:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一個問題又出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.60,0:17:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說羅森費爾特一派嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次開始不是已經將他們從樞機委員會除名了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.30,0:17:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了作為地球人之自豪的貴族連庶民還不如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經站在反貴族的庶民那一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.20,0:18:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 早晚會蔓延到銀河中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,污染每一吋土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也包括我們的地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才建造方舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是建造丟卡利翁的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是令人不愉快呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.00,0:18:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.10,0:18:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就意味著我們將銀河交給了庶民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒辦法啊
